f9d3632c-dad3-4402-8237-12014513a04f.Text:
Against enemies affected by Extrapolation from the Overseer's Servo-Skull Swarm, the Overseer only consumes half the normal number of Exploit stacks.
Affected features include:
-<indent=5%>Attacks and damaging abilities</indent>
-<indent=5%>Tactical Knowledge</indent>
 <indent=5%>When used a single target.</indent>
-<indent=5%>Exploit Weakness</indent>
 <indent=5%>When used to reduce a targets armor to 0%, no Exploit stacks are consumed.</indent>
